The paper deals with the visualization of hypergraphs, which is a topic in computational geometry (cs.CG). It also involves the study of the structure of hypergraphs, which falls under the category of data structures (cs.DS) and discrete mathematics (cs.DM). The paper also discusses the complexity of the problem of determining subdivision drawings, which is related to graph theory (cs.GT) and computational complexity (cs.SI).
